  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself in <strong>Driving Is Hard</strong>! Drive a bathtub on wheels through steep, unforgiving terrain where every mistake costs you progress. Master tough physics-based gameplay, sharpen your patience, and uncover Jeff’s journey of self-doubt, family struggles, and emotional growth as he finds strength, self-acceptance, and hope for a brighter future. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/1aa1cb5c00e0c09277e5d61bff34d39d.poster.avif?t=1774166795\" width=628 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/1aa1cb5c00e0c09277e5d61bff34d39d.webm?t=1774166795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/1aa1cb5c00e0c09277e5d61bff34d39d.mp4?t=1774166795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Drive a Bathtub</strong>: Navigate Jeff in a physics-based bathtub on wheels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Select Your Experience</strong>: Easy Mode for a fun, relaxed time or Hard Mode for the original challenge.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore 7 Worlds</strong>: Each with unique challenges and mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to Play, Hard to Master: </strong>Simple controls, challenging mechanics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Emotional Journey: </strong>Jeff faces his father’s expectations and finds his own path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable Bathtub</strong>: Unlock and use different car skins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collect Soaps</strong>: Find 21 soaps as you play.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WARNING!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This difficult game tests your patience—falling is part of the challenge. Will you rise or quit when it gets tough?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/cf7a8c69af4838936ed5f611a1934114.poster.avif?t=1774166795\" width=628 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/cf7a8c69af4838936ed5f611a1934114.webm?t=1774166795\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175860/extras/cf7a8c69af4838936ed5f611a1934114.mp4?t=1774166795\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
